        </div><!-- blog-post -->

        <div class="col-md-12 blog-post">
          <h2>Express/Secure Handlebars</h2>
          <p>I am using the Express/Handlebars framework...</p>
          <p>You can integrate the Context Parser with Handlebars on Express framework at server side with our <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/express-secure-handlebars">express-secure-handlebars</a> npm package.
        </div><!-- blog-post -->

